        - `tool_call:write_to_file%` — Plant manager must not write files directly
        - `mcp_call:%codebase___retrieval%` — Plant manager must not run codebase retrieval directly
      - Before exiting, run `.kilocode/tools/check_punch_card.sh "$SESSION_ID" "plant-orchestrate"`.
